STATE of Washington, Respondent,
v.
Tye Glen WEST, Petitioner. No. 95258-2 Supreme Court of Washington. FILED MAY 3, 2018

ORDER

¶ 1 This matter came before the Court on its May 3, 2018, En Banc Conference. The Court considered the petition and the files herein. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶ 2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶ 3 ORDERED:

¶ 4 That the petition for review is denied. The State's motion to strike portions of the petition for review is denied.

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J.
